se of ‘Santa Claus’ (an alteration of the Dutch form of his name, <i>Sinterklaas</i>)."],"variants":[{"name":"Nickolas","meanings":["Mainly U.S.: variant spelling of   Nicholas  , influenced by the short form   Nick ."]},{"name":"Nicolas","meanings":["From Late Greek.  See  <b>Nicholas</b> ."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"Nicholas De Avenell was born in 1200, in England, United Kingdom. He had at least 2 daughters with Mrs. Nicholas De Avenell. He died in 1253, in Merevale, Warwickshire, England, United Kingdom, at the age of 53."},"et":{"1200–1253":"1200–1253","1200–Female":"1200–Surnud","1230–1264":"1230–1264","1230–Female":"1230–Surnud","1200":"1200","1221":"1230","1253":"1253","1264":"1264","1230":"1230","Ashington, Somerset, England":"Ashington, Somerset, England","England":"Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Merevale Abbey, Warwickshire, England":"Merevale, Warwickshire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","England, United Kingdom":"Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"1200–1253":"1200–1253","1200–Female":"1200–Kuollut","1230–1264":"1230–1264","1230–Female":"1230–Kuollut","1200":"1200","1221":"1230","1253":"1253","1264":"1264","1230":"1230","Ashington, Somerset, England":"Ashington, Somerset, England","England":"Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Merevale Abbey, Warwickshire, England":"Merevale, Warwickshire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","England, United Kingdom":"Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"1200–1253":"1200–1253","1200–Female":"1200–Décédée","1230–1264":"1230–1264","1230–Female":"1230–Décédée","1200":"1200","1221":"1230","1253":"1253","1264":"1264","1230":"1230","Ashington, Somerset, England":"Ashington, Somerset, Angleterre","England":"Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","Merevale Abbey, Warwickshire, England":"Merevale, Warwickshire, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","England, United Kingdom":"Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"Nicholas De Avenell est né en 1200, à Angleterre, Royaume-Uni. Il a eu au moins 2 filles avec Mrs. Nicholas De Avenell. Il est décédé en 1253, à Mere